ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectSanitary Measures to protect public and animal health in respect of trade in live animals and animal products - European Community RATIFICATION
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the EXCHANGE OF LETTERS concerning the amendment of ANNEX V to the Agreement between the European Community and the Government of Canada on SANITARY MEASURES TO PROTECT PUBLIC AND ANIMAL HEALTH in respect of trade in live animals and animal products.
